  },
  {
    "username": "emollick",
    "nickname": "Ethan Mollick",
    "text": "Some (early) evidence that managers have the highest success rate in using Claude Code for coding.\n\nI have been arguing that management is an AI superpower, as clearly specifying what you want, how to do it &amp; what good looks like is key to using agents. https://t.co/ofbCp3f1QB https://t.co/gu013PM8MO",
    "quoted_tweet": null,
    "url": "https://twitter.com/emollick/status/2067839690158268923",
